Description: migrate window management from GLUT to SDL2
 Replace GLUT with SDL2 for window creation, event loop and OpenGL context.
 Add F key fullscreen toggle using SDL_WINDOW_FULLSCREEN_DESKTOP.
 Preserve native 4:3 aspect ratio via letterbox/pillarbox glViewport in both
 windowed and fullscreen modes. Make window resizable.
